imdb.plot outline: Alongside fiery wife Allison (Apocalypse Meow), troubled friend Tracy (Agent Null) and an eclectic team of real-life superheroes, comic book artist turned real life superhero Illya King embarks on an inspiring journey of altruism while having a heck of a lot of fun doing it.
imdb.title: The Real Adventures of Zetaman
akas: The Real Adventures of Zetaman (United States)
plot: Comic book artist Illya King orchestrates ambitious charity projects as his superhero alter-ego Zetaman.

Alongside fiery wife Allison (Apocalypse Meow), troubled friend Tracy (Agent Null) and an eclectic team of real-life superheroes, comic book artist turned real life superhero Illya King embarks on an inspiring journey of altruism while having a heck of a lot of fun doing it.
